OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain will continue
OL,7,Fovernight across northwest Scotland.
OL,8,FOtherwise, dry and largely clear,
OL,9,Fthough low cloud pushing inland again
OL,10,Finto parts of the west, although not
OL,11,Fas extensive as previous night. A warm
OL,12,Fnight for many.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FRain in the northwest may turn
OL,15,Fheavy for a time. The small chance of
OL,16,Fa shower developing elsewhere, but
OL,17,Fmany once again staying dry and
OL,18,Fpredominantly sunny. Another hot day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
